Text:
So, this is a WINDOWS application?

Offered in the section for MAC applications?  

Awesome...

Additionally, as I am not familiar with CNC mills, the description is odd.  Why would a CNC mill need a DNS client?

I assume DNS does not mean "Domain Name System" in this case?

DNS wrong written, it is a application for DNC = Direct Numerical Control, used in machining

Should not be here anyway.
